{"tid":2426130,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有冇人一齊行山30","createTime":"2021-02-27T22:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T04:42:40.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac1d1f08fbff980ed4d2135b131c0de0cdcce88","tid":2426130,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T22:48:21.000Z","msg":"其實琴日有行山<br />\n大圍行到彩虹<br />\n樓梯+馬路唔敢同人講我係行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n約咗個高手谷谷主一齊行<br />\n佢靚仔又funny<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我行雙牛希望石之窗唔洗排隊<br />\n依家訓唔著行馬鞍山過去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者你地睇下有冇人撞岩路線係到討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f2df6fb4add25b59568afcc621b97016ee7292","tid":2426130,"uid":98381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T23:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cdb2d874a26857983ca1c75b0fa9fe59811a76","tid":2426130,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f2df6fb4add25b59568afcc621b97016ee7292","tid":2426130,"uid":98381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T23:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"無上到馬鞍山<br />\n去行梅花古道<br />\n想睇埋陽元石但十點有團下次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8CEg2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8CEg2D.jpg&h=b317f8e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1a047f05ccdd3caa9ccfa7f002ff658d85240fc","tid":2426130,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"見到樓豬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36cae49c150ab97edda